thread.title_full: Not Socks reviewed by Janine - Kaitaia

author: Janine - Kaitaia
title: Janine - Kaitaia
text: Found the perfect Valentine's card for my partner who lives far away from me. I was not only able to buy the card, but to have a personal message written in by hand and sent to him in time for Valentine's Day. Was also very easy to do from my mobile phone. Love? We has it!
